name: Cupboarding Loose
description:
Use WASD to move about, and Space to jump. Jump on the platforms and avoid enemies to reach the end to advance to the next level.

Cupboard Level Theme: Original Composition
Countertop Level Theme: Original Composition
Outdoors Level Theme:  Raiko - Revenger [NCS Release] Music provided by NoCopyrightSounds
